# .env.example
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TEMPLATE — copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
#
# INSTRUCTIONS:
#   1. Copy this file:
#        cp .env.example .env          (Mac/Linux)
#        copy .env.example .env        (Windows Command Prompt)
#        Copy-Item .env.example .env   (Windows PowerShell)
#
#   2. Get your free API key from data.gov.in:
#        a. Go to: https://data.gov.in/user/register
#        b. Create a free account
#        c. Log in → go to your Profile → find "API Key"
#        d. Copy your API key
#
#   3. Replace "your_api_key_here" below with your actual API key
#
#   4. Save the .env file
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit .env to git! It is listed in .gitignore.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

